%^YELLOW%^Skill: Thievery

%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^A player's thievery skill indicates their quickness of hand. It affects abilities used to steal or place items upon another person unseen, or to hide items upon oneself or within the surrounding area.

%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Stat basis: %^WHITE%^dexterity
%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Current areas of influence: %^WHITE%^stealing, pick pockets, item concealment

%^YELLOW%^This skill is now converted.

%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Related helpfiles: %^WHITE%^skills, steal, pp, hide
